name: Foxboy
description: Here at foxboy, we are creating what we plan to be the leading 3D NFT Marketplace + Gaming ecosystem on the binance smart chain. We are a team of two from both Canada and Norway combining our real life skills to create the best project, combining our real life business/skillset with our love for crypto. By the end of 2021 we plan to have a fully operational marketplace to purchase our NFT models, some of which have already been teased on twitter and telegram, we have shown progression updates of our 3D Artists current work. Once our marketplace is launched, our next step is creating an NFT Gaming roadmap which will include progressive updates on ways to utilize your NFT, from battling other avatars and leveling up - or fighting each other for your tokens!
